name: This spreadsheet contains all of the players that appear on the Top Prospects list for any of the websites listed on 6/23/24.
If a player was unranked on a certain website, he was given the rank equivalent to the total number of players that were ranked on at least one website (that ranked as many players).

For example, if a player was unranked on Bleacher Report's top 50 prospects list, and there are 70 prospects that appear in the top 50 of at least one other website, then the player will receive the rank of 70.
